uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.charts

Class PeriodChart<P extends PeriodPlot>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.charts.Chart
      • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.charts.PeriodChart<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - Type of Plot
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SetPeriodChart, TimeChart

    public abstract class PeriodChart<P extends PeriodPlot>
extends Chart
    PeriodChart is a Chart where the data represents a plot over some period of time. Various PlotStrategies are provided to map the data onto time periods.
    Author:
    spb
    See Also:
